   - Applies to: Documentation, papers, written explanations, test docs
   - Full text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode

2. CODE (MIT License)
   - License: MIT
   - Applies to: Python code in consciousness/, metacognition/, swarm/ modules
   - File: LICENSE.MIT
   - Provides: Software usage, modification, and distribution rights
   - Requires: Attribution and disclaimer of liability

3. EXPERIMENTAL & PROPRIETARY CONTENT
   - Quantum consciousness modules may have specific licensing
   - Autopoietic components may be proprietary
   - See LICENSE.MIT for specific module details
   - Contact author for questions about specific code sections

