WHY THIS STRUCTURE?

Documentation (CC BY 4.0):
✓ Encourages scientific collaboration and reuse
✓ Papers and explanations can be freely adapted and translated
✓ Requires attribution to respect authorship
✓ Globally recognized standard for academic content
✓ Supports open science and reproducibility

Code (MIT):
✓ Industry-standard software license
✓ Clear permissions for commercial and private use
✓ Explicit warranty disclaimers
✓ Well-established in open source community
✓ Compatible with most other licenses

